<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#TSJN-01-07-0435-fn-0001-ptr" id="TSJN-01-07-0435-fn-0001">1</a>
<p>This and subsequent words in italics were written in code and were decoded interlineally by TJ (though with difficulty on account of errors in the code); TJs decoding has been verified by the editors, employing Code No. 5.</p></div>
